        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="mission-planing-for-uav-by-oleg-sautenkov"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#mission-planing-for-uav-by-oleg-sautenkov"></a> Mission Planing For UAV by <a href="https://sauten.tech/">Oleg Sautenkov</a></h2><blockquote><p>此笔记记录Oleg Sautenkov三篇关于UAV-Mission Planing的文章。</p></blockquote><h3 id="mission-planing"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#mission-planing"></a> Mission Planing</h3><p>为无人机设计一条从起点到终点、满足任务要求且最优的飞行路径与动作序列。</p><ul><li><strong>路径与动作</strong>：不仅规划“怎么飞”（路径），还规划“做什么”（动作，如在何处悬停、拍照、传输数据。</li><li><strong>满足约束</strong>：必须遵守任务要求（如避开禁飞区、保持与卫星的通信、在电池续航内完成）。</li><li><strong>追求最优</strong>：在众多可行方案中，找到能耗最少、时间最短或信号最好的平衡解</li></ul><h3 id="uav-vla-vision-language-action-system-for-large-scale-aerial-mission-generation"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#uav-vla-vision-language-action-system-for-large-scale-aerial-mission-generation"></a> UAV-VLA: Vision-Language-Action System for Large Scale Aerial Mission Generation</h3><blockquote><p>主要针对利用卫星图（俯瞰）+ 高层指令输出航点序列（经纬度）</p></blockquote><p><img src="/images/UAV-VLA.png" alt="" /></p><h4 id="problem"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#problem"></a> Problem</h4><ul><li>传统UAV任务规划严重依赖专业操作员，使用地面站软件（如Mission Planner）手动设置航点。</li><li>现有AI方法（VLA/VLN）的局限<ul><li>数据饥渴： 需要大量“语言-动作”配对数据进行训练，在真实、多样的UAV场景中难以获得。</li><li>缺乏全局视野： 许多方法专注于第一视角的导航（VLN），缺乏从“上帝视角”（卫星图）进行全局、高效的路径规划。</li></ul></li></ul><h4 id="innovation"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#innovation"></a> Innovation</h4><ul><li>提出了一个大规模 VLA 系统，输入是“基于文本的任务请求 + 卫星图像”，输出是“路径-动作集”。</li><li>发布了 UAV-VLPA-nano-30 基准数据集，用于在全球尺度下评估 VLA 系统。</li><li>在 UAV-VLPA-nano-30 上验证了系统，结果显示其性能可与人类水平的路径和动作生成相媲美。</li></ul><h4 id="method"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#method"></a> Method</h4><p><strong>UAV-VLPA-nano-30</strong>：从美国地质调查局（USGS）的公开平台 EarthExplorer 收集的 30张高分辨率卫星图像。图像覆盖美国各地，包含多种环境，以确保评估的全面性。</p><ul><li>关键元数据：每张图都带有地理描述信息（经纬度范围等），用于将图像上的像素点转换为真实的经纬度坐标，以便生成无人机可以执行的飞行计划<ul><li>分辨率：约 1.5 米/像素，能清晰看到地面特征。</li><li>覆盖面积：每张图覆盖约 760 平方米。</li><li>拍摄条件：春/夏季的白天，确保光线良好、视野清晰。</li></ul></li><li>人类专家用Mission Planner手动生成的飞行计划。<img src="/images/UAV-VLPA-nano.png" alt="" /></li></ul><p><strong>Goal extracting GPT module</strong>给定自然语言描述<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>I</mi><mo>=</mo><mo stretchy="false">{</mo><msub><mi>i</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo separator="true">,</mo><msub><mi>i</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">.</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">.</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">.</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><msub><mi>i</mi><mi>k</mi></msub><mo stretchy="false">}</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">I=\{i_1,i_2,...,i_k\}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07847em;">I</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mopen">{</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal">i</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.30110799999999993em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight">1</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal">i</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.30110799999999993em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight">2</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;"></span><span class="mord">.</span><span class="mord">.</span><span class="mord">.</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal">i</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.33610799999999996em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.03148em;">k</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose">}</span></span></span></span></p><blockquote><p>For instance:&quot;Fly around all the buildings at a height of 100 meters and come back.&quot;</p></blockquote><p class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mi>G</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>G</mi><mi>P</mi><mi>T</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>I</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mo stretchy="false">{</mo><msub><mi>g</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo separator="true">,</mo><msub><mi>g</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">.</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">.</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">.</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><msub><mi>g</mi><mi>n</mi></msub><mo stretchy="false">}</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">G=GPT(I)=\{g_1,g_2,...,g_n\} </annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">G</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">G</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">P</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">T</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07847em;">I</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mopen">{</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">g</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.30110799999999993em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:-0.03588em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight">1</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">g</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.30110799999999993em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:-0.03588em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight">2</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;"></span><span class="mord">.</span><span class="mord">.</span><span class="mord">.</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">g</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.151392em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:-0.03588em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">n</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose">}</span></span></span></span></span></p><p>G包含根据指令衍生的目标。<strong>Object search VLM module</strong></p><p class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>P</mi><mi>p</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mi>M</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>l</mi><mi>m</mi><mi>o</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>G</mi><mo stretchy="false">